{"tid":1073360,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟放低你隻貓食緊嘅保健品","createTime":"2019-03-22T15:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T03:49:20.000Z","uid":174731,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"10968416923d43ee76b4a986046ddbc29f22e85a","tid":1073360,"uid":174731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T15:22:24.000Z","msg":"大家討論下食過咩保健品係真係有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有好多寫明係寵物用嘅保健品價錢超貴 品質又冇保障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我隻貓食過:<br />\nlysine 係因為佢細個好多眼水所以食 可以保養支氣管 食開有用就一路食落去<br />\n<br />\n魚油 食完啲毛真係滑咗 但係要小心選擇同埋計食用量配以維他命E  如果唔係食用過量會有害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n益生菌 我隻貓腸胃麻麻所以一軟便就要俾佢食 依家食緊汪貓  大家有冇咩牌子推介？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8fb3488.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8fb3488.png&h=c982340d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m1VsNnw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm1VsNnw.png&h=cf2a49ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係騙案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />細個超乖依家好寸"},{"pid":"9da35183a3612d77f0f2136146b27991d132f6f7","tid":1073360,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T15:25:30.000Z","msg":"咁樓主有咩牌子建議？？<br />\n我平日都冇俾過我果隻食所謂既保健品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fca07629324ebfa3947cb0490e1ff757789d1b3","tid":1073360,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T15:26:52.000Z","msg":"Lm睇相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c5342d2e4cdee2657597beeeda4dacc29f120b","tid":1073360,"uid":174731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9da35183a3612d77f0f2136146b27991d132f6f7","tid":1073360,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T15:25:30.000Z","msg":"咁樓主有咩牌子建議？？<br />